00:08:55.340 --> 00:08:56.660
Apologize?

00:08:58.100 --> 00:09:01.060
Besides the Paramount,

00:09:02.140 --> 00:09:03.260
I own a dock in Song City.

00:09:07.820 --> 00:09:08.460
How did you know

00:09:08.460 --> 00:09:10.260
