00:09:31.740 --> 00:09:33.460
I have a shipment.

00:09:35.180 --> 00:09:36.460
I'll use your dock.

00:09:36.940 --> 00:09:38.460
And you'll oversee it personally,

00:09:39.620 --> 00:09:41.260
